          "kind": "person-direction",
          "personA": "silas-blackwood",
          "direction": "NE",
          "personB": "vivienne-sterling",
          "text": "The cocktail waitress recalled Vivienne being down the hall and to the south-west of the distinctive smell of Silas' pipe tobacco."
